"```sql\nSELECT r1.name\nFROM races r1\nJOIN seasons s1 ON r1.year = s1.year\nWHERE s1.year = 2017\nAND r1.name NOT IN (\n    SELECT r2.name\n    FROM races r2\n    JOIN seasons s2 ON r2.year = s2.year\n    WHERE s2.year = 2000\n);\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the names of races that took place in the year 2017 but not in the year 2000. It uses a subquery to find all race names from the year 2000 and excludes them from the results of races in 2017."